(230, 1, '2013-10-12 03:09:13', '2013-10-12 03:09:13', '<div align="left">\r\n\r\nThe Depression and Bipolar Support Alliance Metropolitan Detroit (DBSA) is a self-help group for those diagnosed with Bipolar Disorder or Depression (Unipolar Disorder).\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<p align="left">Family, friends and a variety of professionals are also included and are an important part of our organization. DBSA Metro Detroit is run by the members. We offer hope, support, and education. We are an affiliate of the<a href="http://www.dbsalliance.org/" target="_blank">Depression and Bipolar Support Alliance</a> which has 275 chapters.</p>', 'About DBSA', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-dbsa', '', '', '2013-10-12 03:09:13', '2013-10-12 03:09:13', '', 0, 'http://www.dbsa-metrodetroit.org/wordpress/?page_id=230', 0, 'page', '', 0),
